          <text>
            <![CDATA[ <p><b>Prohibiting Punishment of Acquitted Conduct Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill limits the consideration of acquitted conduct (e.g., conduct underlying criminal charges for which an individual was found not guilty) by a federal court at sentencing.</p>]]>
          </text>
